_sText:
Surf your way through the three stages of the Underworld in this map I spent hundreds of hours on.

Crafted with love for the KSF Halloween Mapping Contest of 2023.

Tier 4,  4 bonuses.

You may experience a seizure when you first spawn into the map, that is normal. It's just pre-loading the soundscapes to in advance to prevent lag during actual gameplay.


Enjoy!
